videos.headline: Wake Forest's Surratt makes grab with hand in his face
videos.description: Sage Surratt makes a nice catch with a Florida State defender's hand in his face for a first down, on a drive that turns into Wake's third field goal on the night.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wake Forest's Surratt makes grab with hand in his face) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Akers walks into the end zone for a FSU TD
videos.description: Cam Akers takes the handoff and walks easily into the end zone to put Florida State on the board vs. Wake Forest.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Akers walks into the end zone for a FSU TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Akers dives into the end zone for his 2nd FSU TD
videos.description: James Blackman throws a short pass to Cam Akers who takes it the rest of the way as he dives for the end zone right before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Akers dives into the end zone for his 2nd FSU TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Wake's Hinton reaches back for impressive one-handed catch
videos.description: Sam Hartman's pass is off target but Kendall Hinton rises and reaches up for a nice one-handed catch to bring Wake Forest down at the 41 for a 1st down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wake's Hinton reaches back for impressive one-handed catch) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Terry hauls in 36-yard TD to put FSU back on top
videos.description: Tamorrion Terry catches James Blackman's deep pass to the end zone for a 36-yard touchdown that gives Florida State the lead vs. Wake Forest.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Terry hauls in 36-yard TD to put FSU back on top) 2019/10/19
